      "confidence": 0.95
    },
    {
      "type": "Physical-layer (possible/contributing)",
      "cause": "R1 Serial0/1/0 shows input errors prior to/at the state change, indicating a possible physical-layer fault or framing errors on R1's interface that could contribute to instability or link failure; however the authoritative administrative shutdown on R2 better explains the link down state.",
      "evidence": [
        "R1 interface status: input_errors=37, admin_state=\"up\", oper_state=\"lower-layer-down\", last_change=\"2026-03-17T14:00:53\" (get_interface_status:R1:Serial0/1/0)."
